headline: Hartford (NYSE:HIG) Reports Sales Below Analyst Estimates In Q2 Earnings
summary: Insurance and financial services company The Hartford (NYSE:HIG) missed Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q2 CY2025, but sales rose 7.7% year on year to $6.99 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $3.41 per share was 20.4% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
